Package: testthis
Type: Package
Title: Rstudio addins and utils for testthat
Version: 0.0.6
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Fleck", email = "stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Stefan Fleck <stefan.b.fleck@gmail.com>
Description: This package automates menial tasks associated with creating and
  running automated unit tests with the testthat package. It also provides
  Rstudio addins for the most common functions, so that hotkeys can easily be
  assigned. Everything in this package assumes that tests for "R/myfun.R" go into
  "tests/testthat/test_myfun.R".
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
  devtools,
  stringi,
  assertthat,
  utils,
  stats,
  testthat,
  magrittr
Suggests:
  knitr,
  rmarkdown,
  rstudioapi
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
VignetteBuilder: knitr
